Sharp MFP Windows® 10 Information


Current Sharp Windows 8® Operating System print drivers are compatible with the Windows 10® Operating System with the following minor limitations:

PC-Fax Limitations – The preview and sent image files may become corrupt when the resolution is set to 200x100 or 200x400 dpi. Please set the resolution of the image files to 200x200 dpi, 400x400 dpi or 600x600 dpi.
Button Manager Limitations – The link for Button Manger to Microsoft® Word Mobile is unavailable. Please use the desktop version of Microsoft Word to print.

 


