MULTI SHARP  

 
 
 




ROTARY MOWER SHARPENER (MS1301)








Fits any power drill. Re-sharpens all types of metal rotary mower blades to the correct angle in minutes without removing the blade from the mower. Also puts back a keen edge on spades, hoes, lawn-edgers and axes, making them much easier to use.






SHEAR SCISSOR SHARPENER (MS1401)








Sharpens most types of shears including stainless steel, long-handled, wavy edge and shears with a single cutting edge. Also sharpens household scissors. Screws onto bench and as the blades are pushed through, the carbide sharpening block regrinds them to a sharp new edge at the correct angle.






SECATEUR/ LOPPER SHARPENER (MS1601)








Sharpens all types of secateurs, pruners, loppers, tree-pruners and pruning knives curved or straight cutting edge. Clamps to the back edge of tool blade and the grinding jig ensures sharpening to the correct angle. The long lasting silicon carbide abrasive puts on a precision sharp edge in minutes.







2 IN 1 KNIFE & SCISSOR SHARPENER (MS1901)








Much wider appeal than just a Knife Sharpener
Household sharpens knives, cleavers, mezzalunas, scissors left & right handed
DIY sharpens utility knives, pen and pocket knives, multi-tool blades
Highly effective Tungsten Carbide sharpening heads restore a razor-sharp edge





 

 
DRILL BIT SHARPENER (MS2001) 








Sharpens all major drill bit types
HSS
Masonry
SDS-Plus
Flat
Centre-point Wood Bits
Sharpens 3-13mm
Regrinds correct tip geometry for each drill type
Restores sharp as new cutting edges






WETSTONE WATERCOOLED CHISEL SHARPENER (MS3001)








Sharpens Chisels & Plane Blades 10-60mm wide to a professional standard
Unique water cooled system preserves steel temper
Leather strop for razor sharp edge
Water-Cooling is acknowledged by professionals to hone the finest edges. This compact system uses a controlled flow of water to eliminate over-heating of the blade edge and loss of temper in the steel.
Simple fill the built in reservoir with water, turn on the power drill and a continuous film of water covers the face of the grinding wheel.





 

CHAINSAW SHARPENING KIT 4.8mm 3/6" (MS1701) 








For chainsaws with a pitch of 3/16 inch (0.325" pitch).
Maintains chainsaw blades as new for years.
Resharpens with removing chain from saw
Kit contains file holder, round file that accurately sharpens the blade to the correct angle and depth gauge, and flat file.
Suitable for Black & Decker, Bosch, Champion, Husqvarna, McColloch, Partner, Performance Power, Remington, Ryobi, Sovereign and Stihl.






CHAINSAW SHARPENING KIT 4.0mm 5/32" (MS1702) 








For chainsaws with a pitch of 1/4 inch and also 3/8' (0.375" pitch).
This size fits most domestic chainsaws
Maintains chainsaw blades as new for years.
Resharpens with removing chain from saw
Kit contains file holder, round file that accurately sharpens the blade to the correct angle and depth gauge, and flat file.
Suitable for Black & Decker, Bosch, Champion, Husqvarna, McColloch, Partner, Performance Power, Remington, Ryobi, Sovereign and Stihl.





 
 













